#   `BUFx6f_SL  ic=1.297  (1.5,10)=8.1/9 (5,10)=11.0/15 ...`
#   means: BUFx6f at the SL corner, input_cap_ff = 1.297. At output load
#   = 1.5 ff and input_slew = 10 ps, cell_delay = 8.1 ps and out_slew = 9 ps.
