# Use these tables to predict ΔWNS first-principles, then apply the
# move-type calibration ratio from <prediction_calibration>.
#
# VT swap: same family+drive across L/R/SL preserves drive strength;
# typical input_cap delta is < 5%. R is slowest, SL is fastest.
#

